Phobia sets com unit to Predicon frequencies, and attempts 
communication.

"Is anybody there? This is trader ship braches to any Predicon unit, 
can you read me? I've travelled a long way in search of friends. My 
ships low on fuel and sustained heavy damage from a temporal 
anomally. I need a place to set down for repairs. I'm awaiting your 
response.
